title: Megadeth Discography (1985-2014)
description:
I got tired of seeing so many incomplete Megadeth discographies, so I decided to create one and make sure that it has every album. I organized everything including the album artwork. I can't seem to find the latest Countdown Live album so other than that, that's all I've left out. If anything else is missing, leave a comment and I will fix it promptly. 

Enjoy!
